[gd_scene load_steps=140 format=3]

; SKY — A CITY IN THE SKY, aerial archipelago above the clouds.
; Major structures:
;   - Dock Island (spawn) — harbor platform with pier, 5 signal flags,
;     lighthouse beacon, ticket booth, welcome signpost, rope rails
;   - Cloud-Temple (hero piece) — marble pillars, central dome, arched
;     doorways (CSG-cut), inner sanctum with altar + star
;   - Windmill (walkable) — 3-level interior via ladder rungs, CSG-cut
;     doorway + windows, 4-blade rotor, observation deck with 1up
;   - Bell Tower — tall stone tower with CSG arched bell openings and
;     a suspended gold bell (climbing goal)
;   - Boss Pillar — hex summit spire with the main star on top
;   - Rainbow Bridge — semi-transparent colored arch (secret route)
;   - Wishing Pool — small water_blue pond with submerged coins
;   - Cloud Tunnel — CSG-cut corridor through cloud mass, wing cap inside
;   - Dragon Perch (easter egg) — big rock with claw scratches + eggs
;   - Floating Gardens — lush grass-covered islands
;   - 15+ Sky islands connected by wooden rope bridges + stone arches
; Content:
;   - 7 cuttlefish, 4 koopas, 3 piranha plants, 1 chain chomp,
;     2 goombas, 1 bobomb buddy
;   - 45 yellow coins, 8 red coins, 3 stars, 4 oneups, 1 wing cap

